---
title: Beef Bun Cha & Garlic Rice Bowl with Rainbow Veggies & Crushed Peanuts
description: We’re taking this Vietnamese classic dish off the streets of Hanoi and putting our own twist on it. Serve up these sweet chilli and
oyster sauce glazed beef meatballs with a mixture of rainbow veggies. The twist is swapping out the noodles for a fluffy rice.
